<h4>Witch's Exerpiment</h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8">
    Once you pick up the Ball in the shed, the Witch's experiment will attack you. It has 4 forms, each stronger than the previous one. You must kill all of them in one sitting so prepare accordingly. Recoil and poison work. 
